<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>9 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RT-8609 SERIES - INSTALL - GEAR SHIFT LEVER HOUSING ASSEMBLY</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="3">
        <title>GEAR SHIFT LEVER HOUSING ASSEMBLY</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Check the shifter housing assembly to make sure shift block and yoke notches are aligned in
                the neutral position (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13029n2">Figure 232</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13029n2" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13029n2" filename="../figg13/G13029N2.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 232. Check Shifter Housing Assembly</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install gasket and gear shift lever housing assembly on the shifter housing, fitting the
                lever into the shift block and yoke notches (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13029n3">Figure 233</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13029n3" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13029n3" filename="../figg13/G13029N3.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 233. Install Gasket and Gear Shift Lever Housing Assembly</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Apply Loctite 242 or equivalent to the bolt threads and install four bolts in the housing
                flange. Tighten the bolts to 35 to 45 ft-lbs. (47 to 61 N&#8226;m) (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13029n4">Figure 234</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13029n4" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13029n4" filename="../figg13/G13029N4.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 234. Install Bolts in Housing Flange and Tighten</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
